	(12,1,'2017-06-26 12:31:16','2017-06-26 12:31:16','[vc_row full_width=\"1\"][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias=\"home_01_slider\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1499502565038{padding-top: 100px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"7/12\" el_class=\"ro-text-appointment\"][heading tpl=\"tpl2\" text=\"Care For Every Stage \" extra_text=\"of a Women’s Life\"][vc_column_text]Our patients are our number one priority. We strive to understand a woman\'s needs and concerns through every stage of life. That commitment has allowed us to develop a full-service medical practice that offers personalized care and services to meet your various needs.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"50px\"][vc_column_text]<a class=\"ro-btn ro-btn-2\" href=\"/about-us\">Read more</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/12\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" el_class=\"ro-form-appointment\"][heading text=\"Make an Appointment\" el_class=\"text-center\"][contact-form-7 id=\"5\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1498578168405{padding-top: 100px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}\"][vc_column][heading tpl=\"tpl2\" text=\"Our\" extra_text=\"Services\" sub_text=\"We provide a full range of high-quality health care services. These are just a few of our highlights\" el_class=\"text-center\"][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][service_box icon=\"icon icon-shutterstock-166641992-converted-42\" title=\"Women\'s Health Services\"]From before puberty to after menopause,\r\na woman’s body is constantly changing\r\nand developing. At each stage of\r\ndevelopment and maturation, there may\r\nbe questions about gynecological,\r\nreproductive, and sexual health.[/service_box][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][service_box icon=\"icon icon-shutterstock-166641992-converted-42\" title=\"Midwifery Services\"]We provide preconception counseling, care during pregnancy and childbirth, normal gynecological\r\nservices, and care of the peri- and post-menopausal woman. With health education as a primary focus,\r\nthis helps prevent problems and assist women in developing and maintaining good health habits\r\nthroughout pregnancy and delivery.[/service_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][service_box icon=\"icon icon-shutterstock-166641992-converted-42\" title=\"Primary Care for Women\"]We offer primary care services from colds\r\nto injuries, and more. We look at your\r\npersonal health history, family history,\r\nlaboratory analysis and physical\r\nexamination to provide the easiest way\r\nto the healthiest you.[/service_box][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][service_box icon=\"icon icon-shutterstock-166641992-converted-42\" title=\"Menopausal Care\"]Menopause is a time in a woman\'s life when her period stops. This happens because the woman\'s ovary\r\nstops producing the hormones estrogen and progesterone. This phase can occur between ages 45-55.[/service_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][service_box icon=\"icon icon-shutterstock-166641992-converted-42\" title=\"Gynecological Obstetrics\"]We specialize in general women\'s\r\nmedical care, diagnosis and treatment of\r\ndisorders of the female reproductive\r\nsystem, and care of pregnant women. We\r\nrecommend women who are either over\r\n18 years of age, and/or are sexually\r\nactive, or those who experience\r\ngynecological symptoms, have an annual\r\ngynecological exam.[/service_box][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][service_box icon=\"icon icon-shutterstock-166641992-converted-42\" title=\"3D Ultrasounds\"]With our ARDMS/AIUM certified staff you\r\nwill certainly have the benefit of current,\r\ncutting-edge, in-utero visualization\r\ntechniques. We will show you exactly\r\nwhat your baby looks like sleeping,\r\nyawning, smiling or even sticking out\r\ntheir tongue.[/service_box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1530156617827{background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=\"200px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"row-testerminal-home-1\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1499501033065{padding-top: 100px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;}\"][heading text=\"What Our\" extra_text=\"Clients Say\" el_class=\"text-center\"][vc_empty_space height=\"35px\"][testimonial_slider posts_per_page=\"2\" show_title=\"1\" show_position=\"1\" show_excerpt=\"1\" show_meta=\"1\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"1\" content_placement=\"middle\" el_class=\"blog-same-height\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1545231546309{background-color: #e8625c !important;}\" el_class=\"idoctor-blog-home1\" offset=\"vc_col-lg-12 vc_col-md-12\"][heading text=\"Latest Blog Posts\" el_class=\"heading-light text-center\"][vc_empty_space height=\"35px\"][blog posts_per_page=\"3\" columns=\"1\" orderby=\"ID\" order=\"ASC\" el_class=\"blog-light\" show_title=\"1\" show_excerpt=\"1\" excerpt_lenght=\"15\" excerpt_more=\"...\" read_more_text=\"READ MORE\"][vc_column_text]<a class=\"blog-view-all\" href=\"/blog\">VIEW ALL</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2018-12-19 15:34:06','2018-12-19 15:34:06','',0,'http://54.69.42.39/?page_id=12',0,'page','',0),
	(18,1,'2017-06-26 12:47:39','2017-06-26 12:47:39','[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1500910626133{padding-bottom: 80px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1500910617860{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"762\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"idoctor-about-us\"][heading tpl=\"tpl2\" text=\"Care For Every Stage of a Women’s Life\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"idoctor-about-text\"]\r\n<h5>Habersham OB/Gyn is here to serve the total needs of women\'s health.</h5>\r\nOur patients are our number one priority. We strive to understand a woman&amp;#39;s needs and concerns\r\nthrough every stage of life. That commitment has allowed us to develop a full-service medical practice\r\nthat offers personalized care and services to meet your various needs.\r\n\r\nOur physicians and staff are here for every need throughout the stages of women&amp;#39;s health. As\r\nObstetricians / Gynecologists, we specialize in general women&amp;#39;s medical care, diagnosis and treatment\r\nof disorders of the female reproductive system, and care of pregnant women. It is generally\r\nrecommended that women who are either over 18 years of age, and/or are sexually active, or those\r\nwho experience gynecological symptoms, have an annual gynecological exam. Many of the conditions\r\nthat affect gynecological, reproductive, and sexual health may be detected early, which, in most cases,\r\nprovides for a more positive prognosis and successful treatment. We also offer primary care services\r\nfrom colds to injuries.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"28px\"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row]','About Us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2018-12-19 14:42:40','2018-12-19 14:42:40','',0,'http://54.69.42.39/?page_id=18',0,'page','',0),
